<!--
	Nonfunctional subdomains:

		- alumni
		- badlands *
		- community **
		- dfd *
		- hoodmuseum **
		- hop **
		- jobs **
		- libcat	(redirects to login)
		- now **

	* Shows briefings
	** Shows www


	Problematic subdomains:

		- arts		(mismatched, CN: *.herokuapp.com)
		- search	(shows www)


	Fully covered subdomains:

		- (www.)
		- arts		(→ dartmouth-arts.herokuapp.com)
		- briefings
		- dimensions
		- library
		- login
		- search	(→ www.dartmouth.edu/~search/)
		- tower
